NOTE ON USE

Gecko is a media-server orchestration tool. It ships with no content sources,
indexers, or trackers configured. Gecko does not host, distribute, or provide
access to any copyrighted material. The user is solely responsible for the
content they choose to access and for complying with all applicable laws in
their jurisdiction. The download-automation components (the *arr stack,
qBittorrent) are general-purpose, dual-use software with substantial
legitimate uses (personal media libraries, public-domain archives, Linux
distribution images, home video collections).
